snippet.title: The Women Debate Whether It's Right To Blame 'The Other Woman' For An Affair? | Loose Women
snippet.description:
Jack Grealish’s love life is still a hot topic as now Love Island star, Amber Gill has entered the mix. Jack’s girlfriend, Sasha Atwood gave him an ultimatum after he allegedly had secret meetings with actress Emily Atack. Jack has also allegedly had meetings with Amber too, but she has vehemently hit back at claims, taking to Instagram to say: ‘I've never been the 'other woman' nor will I ever be!' and told how she had received death threats over the claims.  
From series 25, broadcast on 22/11/21
